<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>about</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b008b, #4b0082);
        background-size: cover;
        animation: backgroundAnimation 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      }

      @keyframes backgroundAnimation {
        0% {
          filter: brightness(0.8);
        }
        100% {
          filter: brightness(1);
        }
      }

      #container {
        position: relative;
        top: 10vh;
        left: 25vw;
        height: 75vh;
        width: 50vw;
        color: black;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeIn 1.5s forwards;
      }

      .card {
        position: absolute;
        height: 101%;
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        color: black;
        transform: scale(0.95);
        animation: scaleUp 1s 1s forwards;
        top: 5px;
      }

      .card-header {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ba55d3, #8b008b);
        color: white;
        animation: slideDown 1s 1.5s forwards;
      }

      .card-title {
        font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
      }

      .card-body {
        animation: fadeInContent 1s 2s forwards;
      }

      .card-footer {
        animation: fadeInContent 1s 2.5s forwards;
      }

      .glow-effect {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;

        border-radius: 16px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #d609d6, #e12cf8, #a755f4, #ba55d3);
        background-size: 400% 400%;
        animation: gradientGlow 10s ease infinite;
        z-index: -1;
        filter: blur(10px);
      }

      @keyframes gradientGlow {
        0% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      @keyframes scaleUp {
        0% {
          transform: scale(0.95);
        }
        100% {
          transform: scale(1);
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideDown {
        0% {
          transform: translateY(-100%);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeInContent {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      .button-container {
        margin-top: 20px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 15px;
      }

      .custom-button {
        background-color: #ba55d3;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        transition: transform 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
      }

      .custom-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        background-color: #8b008b;
        color: black;
      }

      .custom-button:active {
        transform: translateY(2px);
      }

      a:visited,
      a:active,
      a:link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: black;
      }

      #mssg {
        padding: 5px;
      }
    </style>
    <%- include ("common") %>
    <div id="container">
      <div class="glow-effect"></div>
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card-header">More info here!</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">What's this for?</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            Still wondering ;) ? This is a web socket based site built using
            socket.io APIs to understand the logic behind group chatting. So
            cool, I knowww ;) Go on, try creating multiple instances of the site
            and test for yourself. But........get ready to be amazed!!<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />PS:
            such inventions!
          </p>
          <div class="button-container">
            <button class="custom-button">
              <a href="/home">Get Started</a>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer text-muted" style="color: black">
          <span id="mssg">Its meeeeeee Vibhaaaaaaaaa :)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
